overview.en: Cullinan Coin aims to promote diamonds as a more popular new asset by offering a transparent and open online two-sided marketplace that matches buyers and sellers, making diamond trading as easy and convenient as buying and selling other traditional assets such as gold, currencies or stocks.
overview.zh: Cullinan Coin以推动钻石成为更普及的新型资产为目标，提供透明开放的网上双边市场，配对买家和卖家，让钻石交易像买卖黄金、货币或股票等其他传统资产一样轻松、方便。
